.TH btctax-events 1  btctax "btctax manual"
.SH NAME
events \- Discover the reconciliation event references (`ref`s) you pass to the `reconcile` verbs
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBevents\fR [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] <\fIsubcommands\fR>
.SH DESCRIPTION
Discover the reconciliation event references (`ref`s) you pass to the `reconcile` verbs
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
events\-list(1)
List every DECIDABLE event — the imported rows a `reconcile` verb can act on (transfer\-in, transfer\-out, unclassified, import\-conflict, income) — with its reference, kind, date, amount, and decision status. Rows are in ledger (import) order, which is not necessarily by date. Read\-only; writes nothing
